Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a spooky chateau on 3rd street, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean that abandoned house that no one lives in anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, I heard my mom say...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some strange man came out of nowhere and started living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it looks so spooky, no one wants to go near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems we need to scout out that house, like the police would.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's our duty as the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hidden in the famous painter's masterpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this astonishing mystery you think you can see but can't!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really strange to think someone would\Npurposely move into that kind of house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say, I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm actually more interested in the one residing in your\Nhouse, rather than whoever's in this haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Okiya Subaru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he's a Holmes fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're choosing to be illogical, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can lend my house to whoever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's become really pretty here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the one who moved in took good care of the landscape, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, you're giving me a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We agreed it was only valid until today, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two or three more days won't hurt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we have our own schedules!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I can only give you until tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have my own concerns here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had better keep your promise, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Mortgage Company...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:03:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with your nameplate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's trueâ€”there's no name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't placed a name on it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think you wouldn't put your own nameplate, it sure is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could he be up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In such a house...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy died!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he wasn't in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He collapsed at home last night and managed\Nto call for an ambulance himself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although he was acting strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what he was planning to do\Nafter moving into that haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our minds won't be at ease, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With an unsolved mystery lingering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The neighbors said they don't know much about that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he moved in three months before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't acquaint himself with the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seldom left the house, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone said he would always either stay inside to\Nfix up the house or go out to maintain the landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he didn't have a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's here, it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you an acquaintance of the man who lived here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean, you all knew Wada-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a sensei of some kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master Wada Rokurou was a famous\NWestern-style painter representing Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that guy was a painter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you are too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:45.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:50.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm an art dealer that has been handling\NWada-sensei's masterpieces for a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:50.66,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\fad(250,250)\be2}Yagami Keiichi (50)\NArt Dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei said he borrowed this chateau to use as an\Nart studio for painting a new masterpiece, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,There's no time for that, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and find the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:58.99,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fs14}Hayashi Kaoru (25)\NYagami's Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone were to steal them, it would be tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like this was a mystery easily solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About who that person was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what he was doing here, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was painting all the time, it would make\Nsense as to why he didn't go out often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I wonder what kind of picture he was painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We really wanna see, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drop by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because it was only borrowed as an art studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this kid be that man from childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, children?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to see that guy's paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't find any, even after searching the other rooms and upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that someone stole them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, we didn't see any art supplies at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No easels, canvases, paint, or brushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this really is his art studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The perfect chateau!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:35.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,At that place, I'll create a once-in-a-lifetime masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:35.47,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\fad(250,250)\be2}Wada Rokurou (55)\NWestern-style Painter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei absolutely said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't it be that he simply put his art\Nsupplies away after he finished painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's give it one more careful search!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're about to commence the deconstruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"What"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the guy who was arguing with Wada-san yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was arguing with Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Wada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what did you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone has died and you feel lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, forgive me, my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,See, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,With the Beika Mortgage Company, Shishikura is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:21.68,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\fad(210,0)\be2}Shishikura Yasuo (31)\N{\fs12}Beika Mortgage Company Staff
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our company purchased this land three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We decided to demolish this chateau for other use, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when Wada-san came around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He requested to borrow the house from us for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we agreed to let him for just three months, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You "won't leave"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something has come up and changed my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me two or three more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's causing us problems, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already sold this land to another customer,\Nand agreed to demolish this house immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just two or three more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really put me in a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's why those two were fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if he's no longer with us, that means the problem is gone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carry out the belongings and start the demolition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until we've located the painting Wada-sensei mentioned, can you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do now, Shishikura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's help them find the painting as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sounds fun, like a treasure hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you're not going to find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Wada-sensei's final masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just think of the aesthetic value!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's futile, searching for that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Futile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where on earth did Sensei put his painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's strange as wellâ€”this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If painting had been done here, there\Nshould at least be a scent of paint...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can't smell anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's trueâ€”just like the boy says...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Sensei didn't paint anything here after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The remaining mystery revolves around why he borrowed the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just too soft, you can't even firmly refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it looks like nothing came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no painting to begin with, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, we can get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's get this done quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Wada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking for Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We received a message from Wada-san a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It will be complete today, so please come see the painting," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Come see the painting..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wada-sensei actually said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four or five days ago, he mailed this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Due to the weather, it took longer than expected, but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it will be complete by this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be sure to bring Auntie here to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-Rokurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.82,title001,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(100,0)}Addressed To\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\NTohto Beika City, Beika Town\N15-7 {\1c&HB8F2EE&}Kafuuen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Sensei's handwriting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Eguchi-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's your name, isn't it, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's "Kafuuen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:12.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's a retirement home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's the place I work at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:14.58,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\be2\fad(210,0)}Eguchi Mina (24)\NPrivate Health Care Provider
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A retirement home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That you're Takatoo Saeko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I suspected...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's actually something I heard about from Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he often visited a chateau as a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And an auntie of his always took care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He said that auntie was now in a retirement home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.74,CharCard - 2,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(210,0)}Takatoo Saeko (71)\NWada's Aunt
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was always taken care of by Sensei, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since Takatoo-san's injury a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been suffering from amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't even remember who she is anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amnesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even still, Wada-san would take\Ntime out of his busy schedule to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen, dear auntie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm now working on a masterpiece that's just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How exciting is that, Takatoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do bring it here when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd be impossible to bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean it's a big project?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you feast your eyes on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think even you will regain your memories, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gate guarding your memories will swing right open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Sensei actually did work on his final piece in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and tear this house apart to make up for our lost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you couldn't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no paintings?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said you're giving me a hard time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do now, Shishikura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't proceed if there are people inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have other construction sites to get to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't keep going with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go grab some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No point arguing with a wimp like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That good-for-nothing guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I thought we could finally get started...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Takatoo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about we wait here for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't just stay and sit around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing was found in the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt he actually painted one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lied to his favorite auntie who cared for him when he was little?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for working on a painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What reason did he have for borrowing this haunted house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would seem we're back to the same mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for what he did, looks like he only fixed\Nthe house and took care of the landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just ahead of this house, there's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kids finally went home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time for us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's bright and sunny today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's walk our way to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy was trying to dig a tunnel from that house to here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He tried to steal his way into the underground deposit vault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expected something like an underground tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the house to this bank, the direct distance is only about 50 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were to dig 60 centimeters per day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three months would be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He dug away during the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, during the day, he would bring up the dirt and deposit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By doing that, he could make it appear he was gardening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about him fixing up the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Merely camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't look natural if he only worked on the landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd be impossible to bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were stealing billions of yen, it sure\Nwould be impossible to carry around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you feast your eyes on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think even you will regain your memories, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no one out there who wouldn't be\Nshocked to feast their eyes on billions of yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was referring to shocking her out of her amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perfect, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It made my head spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's find the entrance to the tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kids... are back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that man went as far as to fight the mortgage\Ncompany staff in order to keep staying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't go back in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the storage cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's not connected to the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he could have torn up some of the\Nwooden flooring and dug under there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should go check if there's a void under the floor, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not in this room, it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's try elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, they sure are noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:31.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HBAD8DE&\xbord5\ybord5\fad(0,0)\b1}At Aunt Saeko's House
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And stop making messes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"At Aunt Saeko's House"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, if I consider it like this, it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something strange has come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And because of it, we couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've gotta move to the next site.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what about the demolition of this house!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the fault of...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, this house really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was where Auntie lived, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I might have, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In such a beautiful house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Auntie lost her husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She apparently had a pretty rough time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that, she was very wealthy and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Memories from the past when she was fortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to burn it down completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop doing foolish things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if the fire were to spread to the rest of the neighborhood!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But please understand, I have my own duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just one more day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like he's willing to wait one more day to tear down the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could have just done it, and tore it down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, the painting wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no underground tunnels...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the reason that man borrowed this house was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he could work on something for his auntie, Takatoo-san:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A once-in-a-lifetime masterpiece made just for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei's masterpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still in progress, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be complete tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it's bright and sunny... Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\shad1\fscy150\fs14\fad(850,0)}The Next Day\h\N\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is entirely complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gorgeous sea of flowers flooding around the chateau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the masterpiece Wada-san had worked toward for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The masterpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this view!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the bad weather, it took extra time to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why he asked for more days...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takatoo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Know this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers blooming around the garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And swaying in the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there was this chateau...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband stood beside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I was always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The always-cute Roku-chan, my nephew, often came over to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roku-chan lost his mother when he was still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He viewed me as his mother after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takatoo-san, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gate to her memories opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why it had to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chateau that looks so much like her house...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The nameplate was meant to be signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:21:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he couldn't place a nameplate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not until the flowers bloomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, as with any art project, you only put it on after it's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what a signature is for!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's all gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The haunted house, and the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a waste, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.55,0:23:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man's wish finally reached his auntie, so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.23,0:23:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.10,0:23:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't just leave me here, you guys!
